snippet.title: Harvest VR - Ready To Ranch!
snippet.description:
This update is a big one. We've been very busy with loads of bug fixes and ofcourse the new ranch! The "Ready To Ranch" update gives your life on the farmstead a whole new experience with the use of farm animals. These animals can be fed, harvested, or even slaughtered for resources! 

A whole new area, new decorations, new features such as woodcutting, ranching and much more to discover in this new update!

Download our game now for Quest on App lab!
https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/3782210318498800/
or for Rift on the Rift Store!
https://www.oculus.com/experiences/rift/3476156772405821/

Join our Discord community for fun talks and latest updates:

Music in this video is from Zapsplat.
